'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4129] on 4 June 2001 at 5:23:35 pm'!"Change Set:		SqC-Updates-tkDate:			4 June 2001Author:			Ted KaehlerChange the name of the Disney updates to SqC updates.### Caution:  Try to be up to date when you put out a new update.  If you do put out an update from an older image, please tell Ted."!"Postscript:Change the name of Disney Internal Updates* in two places."| list sv |list _ Utilities classPool at: #UpdateUrlLists.list do: [:triple |	triple first = 'Disney Internal Updates*' ifTrue: [		triple at: 1 put: 'SqC Internal Updates*']].(ServerDirectory serverNames includes: 'UpdatesExtAtKitchen2') ifTrue: [	sv _ ServerDirectory serverNamed: 'UpdatesExtAtKitchen2'.	sv group key: 'SqC Internal Updates*'].!